[[File:Capital punishment for drugs world map.svg|thumb|500px|{{legend|#e8aa30|Only under certain conditions}}
{{legend|#cc7662|Capital punishment for drug offenses}}]]
{| class="wikitable collapsible collapsed" style="float:right; clear:right;"
